	manipulate file.
	Use single quotes for strings replaced by configuration.
	* share/bin/suid/access-registration: New program for manipulating
	registration files.
	* share/lib/GradingCommon.pl: Add configurable REGISTER_PROG variable.
	Use single quotes for strings replaced by configuration.
	
